# G1 — every incident-event with its full role-player fanout.
# Studio renders ~22 incident-event nodes, each connected to its incident,
# anchor-time, anchor-location (where present), originating-document, and
# witnesses. This is the canonical view of the n-ary hyperedge primitive.

match
  $ie isa incident-event;
  $ie links (incident: $i, originating-document: $d);
